Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才提到說要初吻而已 結果她就跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還提初吻 你也太厚臉皮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得如果說自己是第一次\N那樣的話印象不是會比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種謊話 人家光靠直覺就能看穿的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而會是那種更讓人不敢信任的典型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定，那時候的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第30話 「裸足的少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能夠烤成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生先生真是什麼都會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃過再誇獎不是比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會烤蛋糕的男人很少見嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好，我是篠原若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是會挑時間的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個蛋糕是曉生先生做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用，不過味道不保證就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生先生真是什麼都會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句話我剛才已經說過了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是請先吃吃看再誇獎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會烤蛋糕的男人很少見嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句剛才我也說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼覺得你是故意漏我氣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你說過\N曉生先生已經有未婚妻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，喜歡的心情和那沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔？是喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在談什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 沒有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那會是少女們的壞心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果一直這麼死腦筋的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是會連戀愛都談不成的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是像個女孩子一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼說是為了你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿這什麼男生制服 可是一點都不好看的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，大家都說這樣挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家說又怎樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的關鍵是我這生活指導老師所決定的品味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算老師這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請教務主任也嚴正的說說她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不遵守校規的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子還是該穿著輕盈飄逸的裙子才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰決定的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這、這不是理事長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉、曉生先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！不，我是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教務主任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的國中部懇親會讓我也參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老早就想和理事長一起促膝長談了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有，理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次提到有關…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去阿姆斯特丹姊妹校的視察團成員人選…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，也許最近遴選委員會就會發出正式的通知了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩請您讓我的名字也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會記在心上的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外，我有點事想找她談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把學生借給我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了…理事長…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是他的容姿… 還是穿著打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，還有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太常以校規為理由去拘束學生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論如何…都請以尊重學生自主性的方式進行輔導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我談的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小傻瓜，沒有什麼事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也是你那身威風凜凜裝扮的迷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再者，你面對那些囉唆的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然不改變自己信念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我感到有某種堅強與崇高…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長可以說那種話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是我妹妹…不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…這樣的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，我在想什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家曉生先生已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺最近好像常看到這部車耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是今年的熱門車款嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐－蒂－娜－
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，篠原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話請不要叫我篠原 叫我若葉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人居然偷偷的一起出場 這可不太尋常喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成等下要約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然碰在一起罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，曉生先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起去兜風呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像今天這樣在這碰到 一定也是某種緣份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明最近每天都跑來玩還敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一輩子當作回憶的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就兩個小時也可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是會強迫人的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准！不准！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐蒂娜不用跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為約會是指單獨兩個人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對，曉生先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔，請慢走…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好美的回憶喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海好漂亮… 風的感覺也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是最棒的約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想你應該也知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生先生可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有未婚妻了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 難得人家正在陶醉的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是兜兜風而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是在吃醋吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這、這才不可能呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早啊，姬宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安，歐蒂娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的明明是王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明只喜歡送我這枚戒指的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我會如此地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡會是這麼的小鹿亂撞呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，你是怎麼啦？ 居然會犯那種錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確…我到底是怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？歐蒂娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…抱歉，還讓你照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是趕快去保健室冰敷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說姬宮啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，歐蒂娜大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，上車吧 去醫院好好檢查一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他事就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓姬宮也一起搭又有什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會是只能單獨兩個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你朋友告訴我的，不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先走了，安希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…曉生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓你陪我一起去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不都已經和家人一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚禮…是在明年春天對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是很好的人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香苗小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是醫生說今天還是不要走路比較好的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦！我還能走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要勉強的好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我背你吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生先生是花花公子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你很會討女孩子歡心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…該說是… 不像理事長的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓人覺得是有點危險的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是不喜歡聽從命令而穿著男生制服嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可能是同類吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的情形… 是因為王子的關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了想和從前就喜歡上的王子重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其背著走，還是用抱的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋鞋鞋鞋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快扔了那雙鞋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要我把重要的紅鞋給…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是穿上的話 你會非跳舞跳到死不可的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道這樣不行 卻一樣會去做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來，你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上也不拿著和我一樣的紅鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這，這個… 我只是拿著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會穿上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不穿還拿在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了！真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都拿著還不穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪費的是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐蒂娜大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您肚子會餓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼問？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看您今天的晚餐 好像幾乎都沒吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有點沒食慾…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若葉那個傢伙她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前若葉那個傢伙說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說沒有不能談的戀愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡人的心情是無法自拔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是有不可以喜歡上的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我並不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也像若葉所說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於喜歡的這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣有著連我自己都不知如何是好的部份在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子的嗎？果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說你也有喜歡的人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有我的王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧你是怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天上歐蒂娜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玻璃鞋的主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一提…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也為她著迷是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決鬥被打敗時，我還大受打擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是因為被打敗的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說居然有個少女動搖了我的信念…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子裡還讓我因此而思考著今後的生存方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有眼光…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會成為好女人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是啊…理事長…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐蒂娜同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天好像沒吃什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是身體不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我怎麼了 這我該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香苗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難得，在這一大早…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這麼早怎麼逮的到你？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近比較忙的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙著看星星嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安，香苗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊，安希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道何時你才肯改口叫我嫂嫂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？你是…那個… 歐蒂娜同學對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃早餐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 倒是說…我母親來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岳母大人來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了，曉生先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岳母大人…真是難得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點話…想和你談談
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是什麼事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作應該都很順利的在進行的才是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是電話裡頭不方便談的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生…\N最近你是不是在躲我的女兒 躲著香苗是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能接手這個學園
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是和我女兒結婚後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有別忘了婚約這種事 是隨時都可以取消的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對香苗小姐一直都很體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至到若是發現彗星的話\N還想用她的名字命名的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聞，這是香苗喜歡的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都擦著她要我擦的香水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在只有兩人的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長還康健吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種男人怎麼樣都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才是喔… 是我的王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說！聽我說！歐蒂娜 我終於見到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生先生的未婚妻鳳香苗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是個漂亮的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人長得美，頭腦看起來也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上她還是個大小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這種人，的確會有小小的贏不了她的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的…可是王子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮我記得你是AB型的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬於讓人摸不清楚\N又不大會吐露心事的類型是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 歐蒂娜大人是B型對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B型是…以自我為中心又非常愛鑽牛角尖…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，真是不好意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來七實為什麼會寄住到我們的房間來？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.13,0:23:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為七實也是B型的關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.07,0:23:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看來的確是非常愛鑽牛角尖沒錯啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回　少女革命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「她的悲劇」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對命運默示錄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
